WEBVTT

00:08:29.497 --> 00:08:32.201
And this is despite a warning

00:08:32.201 --> 00:08:35.624
from the industry's own antifraud experts

00:08:35.624 --> 00:08:38.779
that said that these loans were an open invitation

00:08:38.779 --> 00:08:40.739
to fraudsters,

00:08:40.739 --> 00:08:42.481
and that they had a fraud incidence

00:08:42.481 --> 00:08:44.969
of 90 percent,

00:08:44.969 --> 00:08:47.661
nine zero.

00:08:47.661 --> 00:08:50.728
In response to that, the industry

00:08:50.728 --> 00:08:55.776
first started calling these loans liar's loans,

00:08:55.776 --> 00:08:59.345
which lacks a certain subtlety,

00:08:59.345 --> 00:09:02.395
and second, massively increased them,